com.kuka.roboticsAPI.controllerModel.sunrise.api.OutPort

  • Packages that use OutPort 
    Package Description
    com.kuka.roboticsAPI.controllerModel.sunrise
    Contains the controller implementation for the sunrise controller including it's IO interface.
    com.kuka.roboticsAPI.controllerModel.sunrise.api
    Contains the necessary objects to work with Sunrise.
    com.kuka.roboticsAPI.controllerModel.sunrise.execution
    Contains classes and interfaces responsible for execution of SPRs and high level command by sunrise.
    com.kuka.roboticsAPI.controllerModel.sunrise.mapping
    Contains the sunrise specific mapping algorithms, that convert RoboticsAPI objects to a series of SPRs.
    com.kuka.roboticsAPI.controllerModel.sunrise.predefinedCompounds
    Contains predefined compounds for Sunrise.
